- model the h6 opp points closer to the h616 ones with also more room at the
  bottom to have more room for thermal throttling

- make everything above 1ghz turbo mode as most h6 tv boxes cannot control the
  cpu voltage by some supported pmic regulator and thus thermal throttling is
less effective as it can only scale by frequency and not voltage and this
results in the boxes overheating with time under constant full load, so better
use a lower max frequency as default

